###

### Test KichCo APIs

### Get all KichCo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/KichCo

### Get KichCo by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/KichCo/{{kichCoId}}

### Create KichCo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/KichCo/Create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maKichCo": "KC001",
  "tenKichCo": "Kích cỡ S",
  "trangThai": true
}

### Update KichCo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/KichCo/{{kichCoId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maKichCo": "KC001",
  "tenKichCo": "Kích cỡ S Updated",
  "trangThai": true
}

### Delete KichCo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/KichCo/{{kichCoId}}

### Toggle Status KichCo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/KichCo/ToggleStatus/{{kichCoId}}

### Get Paged KichCo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/KichCo/paged?page=1&pageSize=10&keyword=S&trangThai=active

